<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="it-wont-doesnt-hurt-sb-to-do-sth">it won't / doesn't hurt (sb) to do sth</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>(某人) 做某事也无妨：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It wouldn’t hurt you to help with the housework occasionally.
你不妨偶尔帮忙做下家务。</p></div></div>